---
import BrandbookLayout from '../../layouts/BrandbookLayout.astro';
import SectionLabel from '../../components/SectionLabel.astro';
---

<BrandbookLayout
  title="Brand Strategy"
  pageName="BRAND STRATEGY"
  description="Positioning, target audience, competitive landscape, and brand promise for Reis IA."
>
  <!-- Title Area (Template C: Strategy/Brand — generous spacing) -->
  <section class="relative" style="background: var(--surface-0);">
    <!-- Ambient glow -->
    <div
      class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[800px] h-[600px] pointer-events-none"
      style="background: var(--gradient-blue-ambient); opacity: 0.5;"
      aria-hidden="true"
    ></div>

    <div class="container-standard relative" style="padding-top: var(--space-4xl); padding-bottom: var(--space-3xl);">
      <div class="max-w-[900px]">
        <div class="font-mono text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] mb-6" style="color: var(--accent-blue);">
          Strategic Foundation
        </div>
        <h1
          class="font-bold tracking-tight mb-6"
          style="font-size: var(--text-display); line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.03em; color: var(--text-primary); text-wrap: balance;"
        >
          Brand Strategy
        </h1>
        <p
          class="max-w-[680px]"
          style="font-size: var(--text-body-lg); line-height: 1.6; color: var(--text-secondary); text-wrap: pretty;"
        >
          Reis IA is a high-ticket AI consultancy positioned as the strategic partner for businesses
          that need AI implemented with precision, not experimentation. This page defines the strategic
          foundation behind every brand decision.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="gradient-divider"></div>

  <!-- Section 01: Positioning -->
  <section style="background: var(--surface-1);">
    <div class="container-standard" style="padding-top: var(--space-3xl); padding-bottom: var(--space-3xl);">
      <SectionLabel number="01" title="Positioning" />

      <div class="max-w-[680px] space-y-8">
        <div>
          <h3
            class="font-bold tracking-tight mb-4"
            style="font-size: var(--text-h3); line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.015em; color: var(--text-primary);"
          >
            Not a tool. Not a SaaS. A strategic AI implementation partner.
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.65; text-wrap: pretty;">
            Reis IA positions itself as a premium AI consultancy that doesn't sell software — it sells outcomes. The ecosystem helps businesses implement and monetize AI through direct consulting, scalable systems, strategic partnerships, and community building.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Positioning Matrix -->
        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-[1px] rounded-xl border overflow-hidden"
          style="background: var(--border-default); border-color: var(--border-default);"
        >
          <div class="p-5" style="background: var(--surface-2);">
            <div class="font-mono text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" style="color: var(--accent-blue);">
              We Are
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <li>Strategic AI implementation</li>
              <li>High-ticket consultancy</li>
              <li>Outcome-focused partner</li>
              <li>Systematic methodology</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="p-5" style="background: var(--surface-2);">
            <div class="font-mono text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" style="color: var(--color-error);">
              We Are Not
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <li>A SaaS product</li>
              <li>A low-ticket course</li>
              <li>A tool marketplace</li>
              <li>An AI agency for hire</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="gradient-divider"></div>

  <!-- Section 02: Target Audience -->
  <section style="background: var(--surface-0);">
    <div class="container-standard" style="padding-top: var(--space-3xl); padding-bottom: var(--space-3xl);">
      <SectionLabel number="02" title="Target Audience (ICP)" />

      <div class="max-w-[680px] space-y-8">
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-body-lg); color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; text-wrap: pretty;">
          The Ideal Client Profile for Reis IA is a business decision-maker who understands AI's potential but lacks the methodology to implement it profitably.
        </p>

        <!-- ICP Attributes -->
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div
            class="p-5 rounded-xl border"
            style="background: var(--surface-2); border-color: var(--border-default);"
          >
            <div class="font-mono text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3" style="color: var(--accent-blue);">
              Demographics
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <li>Business owners, CEOs, C-suite executives</li>
              <li>Revenue: R$1M+ annually (or equivalent)</li>
              <li>Team size: 10-500 employees</li>
              <li>Industries: professional services, e-commerce, SaaS, agencies</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div
            class="p-5 rounded-xl border"
            style="background: var(--surface-2); border-color: var(--border-default);"
          >
            <div class="font-mono text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3" style="color: var(--accent-blue);">
              Psychographics
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <li>Believes AI is strategic, not just operational</li>
              <li>Values proven methodology over experimentation</li>
              <li>Willing to invest in premium solutions</li>
              <li>Time-constrained — needs results, not tutorials</li>
              <li>Frustrated with generic AI advice and hype</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div
            class="p-5 rounded-xl border"
            style="background: var(--surface-2); border-color: var(--border-default);"
          >
            <div class="font-mono text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-3" style="color: var(--accent-blue);">
              Pain Points
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
              <li>"I know AI can help my business, but I don't know where to start."</li>
              <li>"I've tried AI tools but can't get consistent results."</li>
              <li>"I need someone who can implement, not just advise."</li>
              <li>"Every AI consultant talks about potential, nobody shows proven ROI."</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="gradient-divider"></div>

  <!-- Section 03: Brand Promise -->
  <section style="background: var(--surface-1);">
    <div class="container-standard" style="padding-top: var(--space-3xl); padding-bottom: var(--space-3xl);">
      <SectionLabel number="03" title="Brand Promise" />

      <div class="max-w-[680px] space-y-8">
        <div
          class="p-8 rounded-xl border-t-2"
          style="background: var(--surface-2); border-color: var(--border-default); border-top-color: var(--accent-blue);"
        >
          <blockquote
            class="font-bold tracking-tight mb-4"
            style="font-size: var(--text-h3); line-height: 1.15; letter-spacing: -0.015em; color: var(--text-primary); text-wrap: balance;"
          >
            "AI implementation with precision. Measurable results. No experimentation."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--text-tertiary); line-height: 1.65;">
            This is the core promise. Every touchpoint — from website copy to client deliverables — must reinforce this commitment to systematic, results-driven AI implementation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
          {[
            { value: 'Precision', desc: 'Every system is engineered, not guessed' },
            { value: 'Results', desc: 'Measurable ROI, not theoretical potential' },
            { value: 'Speed', desc: 'Implementation in weeks, not months' },
          ].map(pillar => (
            <div
              class="p-5 rounded-xl border text-center"
              style="background: var(--surface-2); border-color: var(--border-default);"
            >
              <div
                class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2"
                style="color: var(--accent-blue);"
              >
                {pillar.value}
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">{pillar.desc}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="gradient-divider"></div>

  <!-- Section 04: Competitive Landscape -->
  <section style="background: var(--surface-0);">
    <div class="container-standard" style="padding-top: var(--space-3xl); padding-bottom: var(--space-3xl);">
      <SectionLabel number="04" title="Competitive Landscape" />

      <div class="max-w-[680px] space-y-8">
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-body-lg); color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; text-wrap: pretty;">
          The AI consultancy market is crowded with generalists and tool resellers. Reis IA differentiates through methodological depth and premium positioning.
        </p>

        <div
          class="border rounded-xl overflow-hidden"
          style="border-color: var(--border-default);"
        >
          <!-- Header -->
          <div
            class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_1fr] gap-0 border-b"
            style="background: var(--surface-2); border-color: var(--border-default);"
          >
            <div class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">
              Category
            </div>
            <div class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">
              Competitors
            </div>
            <div class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-[11px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider" style="color: var(--accent-blue);">
              Reis IA
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Rows -->
          {[
            { category: 'Pricing', competitors: 'Low-to-mid ticket, subscription', reisIa: 'High-ticket, outcome-based' },
            { category: 'Delivery', competitors: 'Courses, templates, tools', reisIa: 'Direct implementation + systems' },
            { category: 'Promise', competitors: '"Learn AI" / "AI for everyone"', reisIa: '"AI implementation with precision"' },
            { category: 'Visual', competitors: 'Generic tech/SaaS aesthetic', reisIa: 'Premium architectural dark design' },
            { category: 'Conversion', competitors: 'Multiple CTAs, free trials', reisIa: 'Single path: /agendar or /aplicar' },
          ].map(row => (
            <div
              class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_1fr] gap-0 border-b last:border-b-0"
              style="border-color: var(--border-subtle);"
            >
              <div class="px-4 py-3 text-xs font-medium" style="color: var(--text-secondary); background: var(--surface-1);">
                {row.category}
              </div>
              <div class="px-4 py-3 text-xs" style="color: var(--text-tertiary); background: var(--surface-1);">
                {row.competitors}
              </div>
              <div class="px-4 py-3 text-xs font-medium" style="color: var(--text-primary); background: var(--surface-1);">
                {row.reisIa}
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="gradient-divider"></div>

  <!-- Section 05: Ecosystem Pillars -->
  <section style="background: var(--surface-1);">
    <div class="container-standard" style="padding-top: var(--space-3xl); padding-bottom: var(--space-3xl);">
      <SectionLabel number="05" title="Ecosystem Pillars" />

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 max-w-[900px]">
        {[
          {
            name: 'Builder',
            number: '01',
            desc: 'Direct AI implementation for businesses. Hands-on consulting that delivers working systems, not advice decks.',
          },
          {
            name: 'Systems',
            number: '02',
            desc: 'Scalable AI systems and automation. Frameworks and methodologies that multiply output without multiplying headcount.',
          },
          {
            name: 'Partners',
            number: '03',
            desc: 'Strategic AI partnerships. Working with selected businesses on long-term AI transformation programs.',
          },
          {
            name: 'Network',
            number: '04',
            desc: 'Community and knowledge sharing. A curated network of business leaders implementing AI at scale.',
          },
        ].map(pillar => (
          <div
            class="card-rotating-border rounded-xl p-6"
          >
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="font-mono text-[11px] font-bold" style="color: var(--accent-blue);">{pillar.number}</span>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold" style="color: var(--text-primary);">{pillar.name}</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.65;">
              {pillar.desc}
            </p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="gradient-divider"></div>

  <!-- Section 06: Conversion Rule -->
  <section style="background: var(--surface-0);">
    <div class="container-standard" style="padding-top: var(--space-3xl); padding-bottom: var(--space-3xl);">
      <SectionLabel number="06" title="Conversion Architecture" />

      <div class="max-w-[680px] space-y-6">
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-body-lg); color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.6; text-wrap: pretty;">
          Every page in the Reis IA ecosystem leads to one of two actions. There are no pricing tables, free trials, or multi-step funnels.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div
            class="p-6 rounded-xl border text-center"
            style="background: var(--surface-2); border-color: var(--border-accent);"
          >
            <code class="text-lg font-bold" style="color: var(--accent-blue); background: none; border: none; padding: 0;">
              /agendar
            </code>
            <p class="text-xs mt-2" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">
              Book a strategic call. For prospects who want to explore AI implementation.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="p-6 rounded-xl border text-center"
            style="background: var(--surface-2); border-color: var(--border-accent);"
          >
            <code class="text-lg font-bold" style="color: var(--accent-blue); background: none; border: none; padding: 0;">
              /aplicar
            </code>
            <p class="text-xs mt-2" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">
              Apply to work together. For qualified prospects ready to commit.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="p-5 rounded-xl border"
          style="background: var(--surface-2); border-color: var(--border-default);"
        >
          <div class="font-mono text-[11px] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" style="color: var(--accent-blue);">
            CTA Design Rule
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 1.65;">
            Blue accent color is reserved for conversion elements. Maximum 2 blue elements per viewport. If it is blue, it must be actionable. Blue = "act here."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BrandbookLayout>
